<p class="text" style="text-align: justify; ">As  time and resources permit this section of the CSD website will be  updated periodically to post archived or not previously accessible CIP  and CGIAR materials in various digital formats, and in different  languages.   The first two sections are 1) CIP only learning materials  arising from a recently initiated (mid 2008) CIP Seminar Series which  will be continually updated; and 2) other CIP published or CIP Learning  Resources (Publications, Manuals, Videos &amp; CDs from 1990 to 2009).   In future we plan to revised and update this section of the CSD web-site  posting with online courses, other presentations and special lectures  by CIP scientists.</p>
<p class="text" style="text-align: justify; ">All  materials noted here are available through a simple search within the  CSD site, but we plan to refine the search engine in future to allow  easier access to more data and more complex searches.</p>
